name: Ganjan
description:
The girl's name is Ganjan, she lives in the village of "Zaminan" in Sistan province of Iran, the area where she lives has the least basic living facilities. They walk miles to get water to for themselves. Ganjan has to help his family every day. He is 8 years old and has no dreams!
Technique: oil on canvas, size: 30 x 45 cm, Digital size: 1984 x 2688 pixels
